---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Work Experience
pageDescription: "Samuel Mamootil's cloud engineering career — case studies from Wipro, IBM, LTIMindtree, and NeuroSpeech. AWS, Azure, GCP, Terraform, Kubernetes, DevOps, and AI infrastructure."
---

<section class="section container">
  <p class="eyebrow">Career</p>
  <h1>Work Experience</h1>
  <p class="lead">Each role is presented as a case study — not just a job title and bullet points. Click any card to read the full context, architecture, and outcomes.</p>

  <div class="cs-index-grid cs-index-grid--full" style="margin-top:2rem;">
    {% for cs in casestudies %}
    <a class="cs-card" href="/work/{{ cs.slug }}/">
      <div class="cs-card__header">
        <span class="cs-card__logo" style="background:{{ cs.logoColor }}">{{ cs.logoText }}</span>
        <div>
          <p class="cs-card__eyebrow">{{ cs.eyebrow }}</p>
          <h2 class="cs-card__company">{{ cs.company }}</h2>
          <p class="cs-card__role">{{ cs.role }}</p>
          <p class="cs-card__period">{{ cs.period }} &middot; {{ cs.location }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="cs-card__headline">{{ cs.headline }}</p>
      <div class="tag-list">
        {% for t in cs.tags | slice(0, 5) %}<span class="tag">{{ t }}</span>{% endfor %}
      </div>
      <span class="cs-card__cta">Read case study →</span>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <!-- UTA role — not a case study, shown as a simple card -->
  <div class="cs-card cs-card--plain" style="margin-top:1.25rem;">
    <div class="cs-card__header">
      <span class="cs-card__logo" style="background:#BF5700">UTA</span>
      <div>
        <p class="cs-card__eyebrow">Web Development · Academic</p>
        <h2 class="cs-card__company">UTA College of Business</h2>
        <p class="cs-card__role">Student Web Developer (Part-time)</p>
        <p class="cs-card__period">Jan 2025 – Present &middot; Arlington, TX</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="cs-card__headline">Maintaining web applications, updating content, and supporting high-visibility digital campaigns and college events at the University of Texas at Arlington.</p>
  </div>
</section>

